{"tid":607119,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《向西聞記》張繼聰好撚好笑","createTime":"2018-03-27T04:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T08:45:09.000Z","uid":40279,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a451ffcc0f7b08a5ba22107a6865af265bd0c667","tid":607119,"uid":40279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"「你肚唔肚餓呀，我煮個麵你食吖」、「嘢可以亂食，說話唔可以亂講」、「人在做，天在看」等一大堆熟口熟面對白，這些年來穿梭於不同港劇，並變成「萬能key」，而影視程式hmvod則搞搞新意思，於3月8日首播原創電視劇《向西聞記》，兼且是全港免費睇。<br />\n<br />\n《向西聞記》改編自香港著名網絡小說作家、向西村上春樹歷年來的最佳短篇小說，劇集分成13個單元，期望帶給香港人有創意的電視劇；劇集班底亦為港產史上最強，並由張繼聰主演，他在宣傳片中說：「香港人唔使再忍喇！3月8日，hmvod原創劇集《向西聞記》隆重首播。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/122014_f9f09b1faa3f60e4deb5296d8ec529a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F122014_f9f09b1faa3f60e4deb5296d8ec529a3.jpg&h=d813985c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張繼聰好撚有喜感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/122857_000bca59be483988e5755afbbde60262.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F122857_000bca59be483988e5755afbbde60262.png&h=7d78927b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeb4b892f83a05f177f3c6200114c4aa294c11c9","tid":607119,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8999b95a84e5c495c904147da24f2423f6a9c23f","tid":607119,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"喜你老母感"},{"pid":"48635a46d513686f3e1f2dc38e9fba2f211949e7","tid":607119,"uid":154385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb4b892f83a05f177f3c6200114c4aa294c11c9","tid":607119,"uid":77788,"like"